name: Frida I Love You Headband
description:
Frida Kahlo!

Inspired by Frida Kahlo and her gorgeous array of flowers, a gorgeous arrangement of hand cut  layered flowers in a selection of bold and dreamy reds, fuschia and burnt tangerine create a one of a kind "Frida I Love You" Headband.

Each layered flower is adorned with a gunmetal grey bead or rhinestone, and are placed on a thin headband that is not very tight to wear.

Wear it as a traditional headband or like a crown, this delicate headband is perfect for weddings, special events or that special night out. 

Available in many colour combinations - if you have a colour range in mind, I'm happy to do a custom order. Please send me a message.

name: Roaring Red Headband
description:
Bold. Fiery. Chic. 

A gorgeous arrangement of hand cut layered flowers and printed rolled rosettes create a one of a kind "Roaring Red" Headband.

Each layered flower is adorned with a gunmetal grey bead. Along with the rosettes, they are placed on a thin headband that is not very tight to wear.

Wear it as a traditional headband or like a crown, this stunning headband is perfect for weddings, special events or that special night out. 

Available in many colour combinations - if you have a colour range in mind, I'm happy to do a custom order. Please send me a message.
